| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1145 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 822ccb75-2df0-5ced-84b6-fdd60feff8da"
